# Church Helper Desktop - Cursor Rules

## Project Type
Tauri 2.0 desktop app with React frontend and Rust backend

## Code Style

### TypeScript (src/)
- Strict mode enabled
- Functional React components
- Zustand for state
- Tailwind CSS

### Rust (src-tauri/)
- 2021 edition
- thiserror for errors
- tokio async runtime
- serde for serialization

## Architecture
- React UI: Dumb components only
- Rust: All business logic
- IPC via Tauri invoke

## Commands
- Dev: `npm run tauri dev`
- Build: `npm run tauri build`
- Rust test: `cargo test`

## Guards
- No `any` in TypeScript
- No `unwrap()` in production Rust
- UI components have no logic
- Secrets via environment only
